Create progress bar.

Source: R/create_pb.R
create_pb.Rd

Create progress bar.

Usage

create_pb(x, .message = TRUE)

Examples

granatlib::create_pb(100)
#> pb created
for (i in 1:100) {
  Sys.sleep(.1)
  pb$tick()
}
